data.description: Enjoy this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath condo in the gated community of The Courts of Doral. Property features new hardwood floor in common areas and new carpet in bedrooms. Kitchen features new fridge and dishwasher. In-unit new combo washer/dryer. Located on the 2nd floor with balcony overlooking beautiful lake view. 2 assigned parking spaces and plenty of guest parking. Military relocation sale. Book your appointment today!
